# Implementation

**Server-first** — `"use client"` only when needed.

**Action-first:** `src/app/action/<segment>/` mirrors routes — one mutation per file. `app/api/` = auth + read-only GET only.

**Suspense:** only slices that use request APIs (`cookies`, `headers`, `connection`, …). Static / `'use cache'` shells stay **outside** Suspense.

**Session:** `auth-session.ts` only — request-scoped `cache()`; never `use cache` / revalidate session. Dashboard: `requireAuthSession()` without `redirectTo` under `dashboard/layout`.

**Cache:** [caching.mdc](.cursor/rules/caching.mdc) / [caching.md](docs/agents/caching.md).

**Detail (Read):** [docs/agents/implementation.md](docs/agents/implementation.md).
